One of the groups within the ruling All Progressives Congress (APC) affiliated with the party’s National Leader and presidential flag bearer for next year’s election, Asiwaju Bola Ahmed Tinubu, Think Tinubu Movement has congratulated its principal on his victory at the recent presidential primary of the party. A statement by its National Coordinator, Chief Segun Balogun Afolorunikan said Tinubu’s emergence as the APC flag bearer is a manifestation of the voice of the delegates that participated in the contest and Nigerians in general. He said it is crystal clear that Asiwaju is the man the cap fits.   ‘Southeast must tap into Tinubu presidency’     Cleric: Muslim-Muslim ticket is not bad     APC support group promises Tinubu 50 million votes   Afolorunikan added: “It is evident on your track record that Asiwaju Bola Tinubu is a man of the people, a unifier, national icon, detribalized, focused, nation builder, visionary strategist and above all, a lover of humanity. “With God on your side, our collective hard work and the will of the masses, we shall record another landslide victory in the forthcoming general elections in your distinguished honour as the next president and commander in chief of the armed forces.”